'''軟殼蟹'''，是剛剛{{link-en|蛻皮|Ecdysis|換殼}}，新[[外骨骼|外殼]]還是柔軟狀態的[[螃蟹|螃蟹]]<ref>{{cite book |author=CiCi Williamson, Garry Pound & Willard Scott |year=2008 |title=The Best of Virginia Farms Cookbook and Tour Book: Recipes, People, Places |publisher=[[Menasha_Ridge_Press|Menasha Ridge Press]] |isbn=978-0-89732-657-5 |chapter=Shellfish and fish |pages=60–87 |url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=pnuFW6zT0T8C&pg=PA63 |access-date=2014-11-04 |archive-date=2020-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200226043915/https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=pnuFW6zT0T8C&pg=PA63 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。除了[[口器|口器]]、[[鰓|鰓]]及[[腹部|腹部]]，整隻蟹都可以食用<ref>{{cite book |author=Tracy Barr |year=2011 |title=Cast Iron Cooking For Dummies |publisher=[[John_Wiley_&_Sons|John Wiley & Sons]] |isbn=9781118053188 |chapter=Soft-shell crabs |pages=137–138 |url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=1w7nI_KRoX4C&pg=PT137 |access-date=2014-11-04 |archive-date=2020-02-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200215024249/https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=1w7nI_KRoX4C&pg=PT137 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。通常以[[油炸|油炸]]方式烹調，炸好的軟殼蟹可以用來製作[[壽司|壽司]]或[[手卷|手卷]]<ref name="Mouritsen">{{cite book |author=Ole G. Mouritsen |year=2009 |title=Sushi: Food for the Eye, the Body and the Soul |publisher=[[Springer_Science+Business_Media|Springer]] |isbn=978-1-4419-0617-5 |chapter=Sushi à la carte |pages=202–250 |url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=RJxuV-0eT4UC&pg=PA226 |access-date=2014-11-04 |archive-date=2020-02-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200215204422/https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=RJxuV-0eT4UC&pg=PA226 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

